Name: git_semver
Version: 0.1.2
Summary: Semantic versions management integrated to git.
Home-page: https://github.com/hartym/git-semver
Author: UNKNOWN
Author-email: UNKNOWN
License: Apache License, Version 2.0
Download-URL: https://github.com/hartym/git-semver/archive/0.1.2.tar.gz
Description: git-semver
        ==========
        
        Install
        :::::::
        
            pip install git-semver
        
        Usage
        :::::
        
            $ git semver -h
            usage: git-semver [-h] [--next-patch] [--next-minor] [--next-major]
        
            optional arguments:
              -h, --help        show this help message and exit
              --next-patch, -p
              --next-minor, -m
              --next-major, -M
        
            $ git semver
            0.1.0
        
            $ git semver --next-patch
            0.1.1
        
            $ git semver --next-minor
            0.2.0
        
            $ git semver --next-major
            1.0.0
Platform: UNKNOWN
